This doctrine is the ſinke of Sodome, the fleſh is the matter, ye burning luſt is a preamble of the fire falling from heauen, &amp; the iuſtice of God threatneth euerlaſting fire &amp; torments for ſuch Mahometical Sodomits. They are ielous ouer their wiues, whoſe faces, when they go abroad are couered, leaſt theſe fiery people be therewith inflamed. Mahomet (ſaith Coelius) had 40.
