the corps to be worſhipped, his anniuerſary or yerely remembrance to bee ſolē
               nized, pilgrimage from all places to be made to the temple of Mecha, where he lieth cheſted, the Saracenicall pilgrims haue promiſe of ſantitye and righteouſneſſe by viſiting his: Sepulchre 

